<i>adverb</i>: 슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍], 슬쩍 [슬쩍], 소폭 [소ː폭], 살짝살짝 [살짝쌀짝], 살짝 [살짝], 사르르 [사르르], 빠끔히 [빠끔히], 빠끔 [빠끔], 달싹 [달싹], 가벼이 [가벼이] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>슬쩍슬쩍 [슬쩍쓸쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and lightly without much effort..</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Little by little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession and quietly so that others do not know..</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 잇따라 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>In succession, carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>슬쩍 [슬쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dd>5. roughly; cursorily</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 들이지 않고 빠르게 대충.</dd><br>
<dd>Carelessly and quickly.</dd><br>
<dt>소폭 [소ː폭]</dt><br>
<dd>slightly; by a small margin</dd><br>
<dd>적은 정도로.</dd><br>
<dd>To a small degree.</dd><br>
<dt>살짝살짝 [살짝쌀짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 잇따라 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly in succession so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 잇따라 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly in succession without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간씩.</dd><br>
<dd>Bit by bit and not much.</dd><br>
<dd>4. quietly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 잇따라 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly in succession so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt>살짝 [살짝]</dt><br>
<dd>1. stealthily; secretly; furtively</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 보지 못하게 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly so that others cannot see.</dd><br>
<dd>2. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 들이지 않고 가볍게.</dd><br>
<dd>Lightly without much effort.</dd><br>
<dd>3. slightly; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>심하지 않게 아주 약간.</dd><br>
<dd>A little, not severely.</dd><br>
<dd>4. on the quiet; stealthily</dd><br>
<dd>드러나지 않게 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others do not know.</dd><br>
<dt>사르르 [사르르]</dt><br>
<dd>1. of itself</dd><br>
<dd>얽히거나 뭉쳤던 것이 저절로 부드럽게 풀리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that something tangled or lumped is gently disentangled by itself.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in the manner of melting away</dd><br>
<dd>눈이나 얼음 등이 저절로 녹는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner in which snow, ice, etc., melt naturally.</dd><br>
<dd>3. unconsciously</dd><br>
<dd>졸음이나 어떤 분위기에 살며시 빠져드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of falling asleep or quietly slipping into a certain mood.</dd><br>
<dd>4. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>눈을 살며시 감거나 뜨는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of opening or closing one's eyes lightly.</dd><br>
<dd>5. softly; gently</dd><br>
<dd>살며시 조용하게 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of moving stealthily and quietly.</dd><br>
<dd>6. tremblingly</dd><br>
<dd>가볍고 힘없이 떨리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of trembling lightly and feebly.</dd><br>
<dd>7. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>배 등 몸의 일부가 조금씩 아픈 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which a part of one's body such as the stomach aches a little.</dd><br>
<dt>빠끔히 [빠끔히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. deeply; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>작은 구멍이나 틈 등이 깊고 또렷하게 나 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a small hole, crack, etc., being deep and noticeable.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>문 등이 살며시 조금 열리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a door, etc., opening slightly without a sound.</dd><br>
<dd>3. through an opening</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 작은 틈이나 구멍 사이로 조금만 보이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing something being seen a little, through a small crack or hole.</dd><br>
<dt>빠끔 [빠끔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. deeply; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>작은 구멍이나 틈 등이 깊고 또렷하게 나 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a small hole, crack, etc., being deep and noticeable.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>문 등이 살며시 조금 열리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a door, etc., opening slightly without a sound.</dd><br>
<dd>3. through an opening</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 작은 틈이나 구멍 사이로 조금만 보이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing something being seen a little, through a small crack or hole.</dd><br>
<dt>달싹 [달싹]</dt><br>
<dd>1. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>가벼운 물건이 살짝 떠서 들려 있는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of a light thing lifted slightly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 입술 등이 살짝 한 번 들리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of one's body, lips, etc., being lifted slightly.</dd><br>
<dt>가벼이 [가벼이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>무게를 적게.</dd><br>
<dd>With little weight.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lightly; rashly</dd><br>
<dd>맡은 일의 비중이나 가치, 책임 등이 낮거나 적게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the importance, value, responsibility, etc., of one's given task is low or less.</dd><br>
<dd>3. lightly; slightly</dd><br>
<dd>죄나 실수, 손해 등이 심하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that a crime, mistake, damage, etc., is not serious.</dd><br>
<dd>4. rashly; indiscreetly</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 말, 행동이 진지하지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one's thinking, speech or behavior is not serious.</dd><br>
<dd>5. lightly; simply</dd><br>
<dd>부담이 되지 않도록 간단하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the action does not become a burden.</dd><br>
<dd>6. lightly; easily</dd><br>
<dd>대수롭지 않게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that one considers something easy.</dd><br>
<dd>7. easily; effortlessly</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 들지 않고 쉽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without trouble or effort.</dd><br>
<dd>8. slightly</dd><br>
<dd>일렁이거나 흔들리는 정도가 약하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the degree of wavering or swaying is weak.</dd><br>
<dd>9. simply</dd><br>
<dd>옷차림이나 화장이 요란하지 않고 활동하기에 편하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the clothes and make-up are not too dressy but are instead comfortable for activities.</dd><br>
<dd>10. easily; lightly</dd><br>
<dd>몸의 움직임이 재빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the movement of the body is quick.</dd><br>
<dd>11. lightly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 편하고 경쾌하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In such a manner that the mind is comfortable and joyful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>